==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lying-in
<hw>Ly"ing-in"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
state attending, and consequent to, childbirth; confinement; <as>as, a
<ex>lying-in</ex> hospital</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act of bearing a child.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lyingly</ent>⟦br⟧
